---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const serviceSchema = {
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "Service",
  "serviceType": "Nonprofit Content Copywriting",
  "provider": {
    "@type": "Organization",
    "name": "Love Your Words",
    "url": "https://www.loveyourwords.com"
  },
  "areaServed": "US",
  "description": "Donor retention email sequences, brand voice guides, and editorial calendars for nonprofits and mission-driven organizations.",
  "url": "https://www.loveyourwords.com/services"
};

const offerSchema = {
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "Offer",
  "name": "Customer Journey Content Package",
  "description": "Retention email system, brand voice guide, editorial calendar and strategy, and an optional testimonial and social proof campaign, delivered as one integrated system.",
  "seller": {
    "@type": "Organization",
    "name": "Love Your Words",
    "url": "https://www.loveyourwords.com"
  },
  "url": "https://www.loveyourwords.com/services"
};

const breadcrumbSchema = {
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
  "itemListElement": [
    {
      "@type": "ListItem",
      "position": 1,
      "name": "Home",
      "item": "https://www.loveyourwords.com"
    },
    {
      "@type": "ListItem",
      "position": 2,
      "name": "Services",
      "item": "https://www.loveyourwords.com/services"
    }
  ]
};
---

<BaseLayout title="Nonprofit Content Services and Donor Retention" description="Donor retention email sequences, brand voice guides, and editorial calendars for nonprofits, written from the stories only your team can tell.">
  <Fragment slot="schema">
    <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(serviceSchema)} />
    <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(offerSchema)} />
    <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(breadcrumbSchema)} />
  </Fragment>
  <style>
    .services-header {
      padding: 80px 6% 60px;
      text-align: center;
      background: #F7F4FE;
    }
    .services-header h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      color: #1C1830;
    }
    .services-header p {
      max-width: 700px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      font-size: 1.125rem;
      color: rgba(28,24,48,0.70);
      line-height: 1.75;
    }
    .featured-service {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 60px auto;
      padding: 0 6%;
    }
    .featured-service h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      color: #1C1830;
      font-family: 'Outfit', system-ui, sans-serif;
    }
    .featured-service p {
      font-size: 1.0625rem;
      line-height: 1.8;
      color: #1C1830;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .includes {
      background: #FEF4FA;
      padding: 32px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      margin: 32px 0;
    }
    .includes h3 {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      color: #1C1830;
      font-family: 'Outfit', system-ui, sans-serif;
    }
    .includes ul {
      margin-left: 24px;
    }
    .includes li {
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      font-size: 1.0625rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .services-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
      gap: 24px;
      margin: 60px auto;
      max-width: 900px;
      padding: 0 6%;
    }
    .service-card {
      padding: 32px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(123,82,200,0.12);
      border-radius: 14px;
      background: #fff;
      transition: all 0.2s;
    }
    .service-card:hover {
      border-color: #7B52C8;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(123,82,200,0.08);
    }
    .service-card h3 {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      color: #1C1830;
      font-family: 'Outfit', system-ui, sans-serif;
    }
    .service-card p {
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: rgba(28,24,48,0.70);
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }
    .cta-section {
      padding: 60px 6%;
      text-align: center;
      background: #F7F4FE;
    }
    .cta-section h2 {
      max-width: 700px;
      margin: 0 auto 24px;
      font-size: 1.75rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-family: 'Outfit', system-ui, sans-serif;
    }
    .cta-section p {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto 32px;
      color: rgba(28,24,48,0.70);
      line-height: 1.75;
      font-size: 1.0625rem;
    }
    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 13px 36px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #7B52C8, #D87DB0);
      color: #fff;
      border-radius: 40px;
      font-family: 'Outfit', system-ui, sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: opacity 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
    }
    .btn:hover { opacity: 0.9; transform: translateY(-2px); }
  </style>

  <section class="services-header">
    <h1>Services</h1>
    <p>Content built from the things only your organization could know.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="featured-service">
    <h2>Customer Journey Content Package</h2>
    <p>This is the complete system. One integrated offering that works because the pieces talk to each other.</p>

    <div class="includes">
      <h3>What's Included</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Retention Email System:</strong> A sequence of emails that shows your supporters what their support actually does. Written for impact, so the reader sees the difference they made.</li>
        <li><strong>Brand Voice Guide:</strong> Your organization's actual voice, written down and formalized, so every team member sounds like you.</li>
        <li><strong>Editorial Calendar & Strategy:</strong> A 6-month map of what to say and when to say it, built from your real stories.</li>
        <li><strong>Testimonial & Social Proof Campaign (optional):</strong> The stories of people you've served, gathered and shaped into proof you can use across email and web.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <p>These pieces work as a system. Your emails reflect your voice. Your voice guides your editorial calendar. Your calendar keeps you consistent. And consistency keeps your people close.</p>
    <p>The result: supporters feel like they know you. And people come back to the ones they know.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="featured-service" style="margin-top: 0;">
    <h2>Customer Journey Copywriting</h2>
    <p>Every stop on your customer's journey needs words. The welcome email. The thank-you page. The newsletter. The donor letter. The web page that explains why you exist. Hire one writer who knows the whole road, and every piece gets written with the rest of your journey in mind.</p>
    <p>Start with the piece your organization needs most. The system can come later.</p>
  </section>

  <section style="padding: 60px 6%; background: #FEF4FA;">
    <h2 style="text-align: center; max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto 48px; font-size: 1.75rem; font-weight: 700; font-family: 'Outfit', system-ui, sans-serif;">Or Start With One</h2>
    <div class="services-grid">
      <div class="service-card">
        <h3>Retention Email Sequence</h3>
        <p>4-6 emails that turn one-time supporters into repeat ones. Each one shows a different dimension of impact.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="service-card">
        <h3>Brand Voice Guide</h3>
        <p>A written guide to your organization's voice: tone, vocabulary, story structure, and real examples. For consistency across all channels.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="service-card">
        <h3>Editorial Calendar & Strategy</h3>
        <p>A 6-month content map with themes, topics, and story angles that build from your real work.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="service-card">
        <h3>Testimonial & Social Proof Campaign</h3>
        <p>The outcomes you watch happen every day, gathered into stories that honor the people you've served.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section style="padding: 64px 6%; background: #F7F4FE;">
    <div style="max-width: 780px; margin: 0 auto;">
      <h2 style="font-size: 1.75rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 24px; font-family: 'Outfit', system-ui, sans-serif;">How We Work Together</h2>

      <p style="font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.85; margin-bottom: 16px;">Retention copy gets built together. The words work because they are your story. True and real.</p>

      <h3 style="font-size: 1.15rem; font-weight: 700; margin: 32px 0 12px; color: #7B52C8; font-family: 'Outfit', system-ui, sans-serif;">What the partnership looks like</h3>
      <p style="font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.85; margin-bottom: 16px;">You stay in the room. You bring the stories, answer the questions only you can answer, read every draft, and say so when a line sounds unlike you. Your people can tell when the words come from someone who was there. Projects run on schedule when that partnership holds, and drafts that sit unread move deadlines with them.</p>

      <h3 style="font-size: 1.15rem; font-weight: 700; margin: 32px 0 12px; color: #7B52C8; font-family: 'Outfit', system-ui, sans-serif;">Your customers are the heroes</h3>
      <p style="font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.85; margin-bottom: 16px;">Retention copy is the copy that pays for itself. It grows from how you already serve: real problems solved, thank-yous that feel personal. The customer becomes the hero of the story, and your organization becomes the guide. From there the journey maps itself. You loved this project, so here's the news about what comes next.</p>

      <h3 style="font-size: 1.15rem; font-weight: 700; margin: 32px 0 12px; color: #7B52C8; font-family: 'Outfit', system-ui, sans-serif;">The copy gets better with use</h3>
      <p style="font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.85; margin-bottom: 16px;">Words are a first draft of a relationship. Once a piece goes out, your numbers tell us what landed: opens, replies, renewals, second gifts. You know your data better than anyone. Bring it, and we test a headline or tighten an ask until the copy earns its keep.</p>

      <h3 style="font-size: 1.15rem; font-weight: 700; margin: 32px 0 12px; color: #7B52C8; font-family: 'Outfit', system-ui, sans-serif;">Your stories stay yours</h3>
      <p style="font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.85; margin-bottom: 16px;">Seventeen and a half years in bank legal work taught me fiduciary duty and the weight of compliance. People's private matters stay private. Names and personal details stay out of the work unless you approve them. Your stories remain your property, start to finish. And copy that touches regulated ground gets written with your rules in mind.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-section">
    <h2>Ready to Talk About Your Content?</h2>
    <p>Every organization has a real story. Let's find the words for yours.</p>
    <a href="/discovery-call" class="btn">Schedule a Discovery Call</a>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
